headline: Equifax Introduces Optimal Path™ Interactive Score Planner
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) is leveraging the power of the Equifax Cloud™ and patented EFX.AI capabilities to introduce the new Optimal Path™ interactive score planner. Optimal Path is designed to help financial institutions, employers, benefits providers, and other organizations provide consumers with personalized, actionable credit score plans within their existing consumer financial health initiatives and platforms.
